item.title: Imperial has talent
item.author: Anisa Nomaan,
item.description: 10 acts, 3 judges, 1 night and a whole lot of fun! This year’s Imperial’s Got Talent has proved to be bigger and better than ever before and has raisedover £1700 for IC Save the Children. Our finalists gave us an amazing show with joint third place going to Jessica Haddon and Esther Berry …
